{"tid":355154,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不滿向教局投訴　恫嚇趕學生出校 興德校長涉威脅家長　拍「自願捐款」片","createTime":"2017-08-11T05:25:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-11T06:51:37.000Z","uid":25125,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d4081dda1d23a4459097ac75598649a908cec0c0","tid":355154,"uid":25125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T05:25:50.000Z","msg":"不滿向教局投訴　恫嚇趕學生出校<br />\n興德校長涉威脅家長　拍「自願捐款」片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】興德學校醜聞越揭越多，有家長向《蘋果》投訴，稱早前向教育局投訴學校捐款問題後，被校長陳章萍恫嚇趕出校「再搞事不能在這裏讀書」，更威脅他即場拍片及撰寫聲明，證明是自願捐款；事後其就讀小四的兒子疑被針對，除在課室被老師當眾辱罵、參加課外活動亦被諸多刁難。重案組昨午到該校檢走教師招聘文件及影子學生的請假信正本助查。<br />\n記者：梁御和<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20170811/large/a0401a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170811%2Flarge%2Fa0401a.gif&h=2d612ca0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■陳章萍校長被指屢游說家長付款，在學校特刊內買全版廣告。<br />\n<br />\n興德學校在2014年曾以出版60周年紀念特刊為由向家長籌款。本身是內地人的家長胡女士指，由於她經常回校做義工，每遇到陳章萍便被對方游說捐款，終答應捐出6,000元、以其兒子名義購買特刊內的一個全版版位作鳴謝廣告。<br />\n<br />\n特刊拖延近3年仍未出版，校方也沒向家長解釋，胡於是向教育局投訴。直至5月，胡的前夫到校接送兒子，<span style=\"color: red;\">陳章萍即上前恫嚇「叫你太太不要再搞事，再搞事小朋友就不能在這裏讀書」</span>。胡稱，兒子當時就站在父親旁，被陳嚇了一跳。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">其後，胡的前夫被帶入房間，陳再要求他拍片證明自己是自願捐款，又叫他即場寫聲明</span>，「如果你不寫，在白紙上簽名也可以」。胡的前夫當場拒絕，與陳爭執一番後帶兒子離去。<br />\n<br />\n事後，胡女士發現其子開始逃避上學，再三查詢才得知兒子懷疑被老師針對。<span style=\"color: red;\">據其子覆述，試過病假後上學，被老師當著全班面前罵他「騙人，講大話，不是生病」；參加童軍活動則被老師阻止宣誓，「他一直期待宣誓做童軍，還帶了不少糖果與同學分享，負責老師卻不將宣誓紙派給他，只有他一個不能宣誓」。</span>胡女士曾與負責老師理論，惟對方敷衍了事。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20170811/large/a0401b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170811%2Flarge%2Fa0401b.gif&h=a3ee2b43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■胡女士指她曾向教局投訴陳校長，之後其子在校內被針對。<br />\n<br />\n被指在教員室裝錄音CCTV<br />\n<br />\n至6月，胡再就事件向教育局投訴，同時考慮安排兒子轉校，「在我們來說香港是先進地方，現在發生這些事就像封建社會一樣&hellip;&hellip;強迫別人簽名攝像證明自己不是被迫，太過份了」。教育局回覆指，早前接獲有關家長就事件投訴，但對方其後表示撤銷投訴，局方將再聯絡該家長了解。興德截稿未有回覆。<br />\n此外，興德學校早前亦被揭發以閉路電視監視老師。有3年前離職的前教師昨接受電台訪問，稱2013年確有失竊發生，校方在茶水間、教員室及操場等地方安裝約十台閉路電視。而工友安裝時懷疑因向教職員透露閉路電視有錄音功能，被陳章萍召喚到校長室責罵。該老師形容，校長在校內很強勢，鮮會接受其他人意見。他又指校董會偏向支持校長，過去曾有其他同事投訴均不得要領，相信包括教育局等不同機構都有收過投訴。<br />\n<br />\n轉貼自: <a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170811/20118041\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170811%2F20118041&d=z8dbsKDF79XyMcAhQQKKbf%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=aeca1319\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170811%2F20118041&h=d5165362\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170811/20118041</a><br />\n<br />\n有權力既女人恐怖<br />\n有權力既肥女人更加恐怖"},{"pid":"6bf360d81754e40c832b16ce4f1ba3d0b9c554b3","tid":355154,"uid":25125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T05:33:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d36cb3d34f370dbf69cac2d835dbe69f685579f8","tid":355154,"uid":761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T05:38:07.000Z","msg":"肥婆死全家"},{"pid":"bfa8578d5a788109834f85df830ef03ce6b1b003","tid":355154,"uid":14070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T05:41:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dc2c8b519af2ac430443ae216926da0fe7bed2c","tid":355154,"uid":90183,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T05:44:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20170811/large/a0401a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170811%2Flarge%2Fa0401a.gif&h=2d612ca0&s={SIZE}\" /> </blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/cTmbnsX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FcTmbnsX.jpg&h=942dd680&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c8d4b650487ec229633a6ffb244597d27364a700","tid":355154,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T05:44:47.000Z","msg":"真係有執政能力既女人太少<br />\n之後話可以上高位既女人數量少既歧視<br />\n可以上到高位既女人都好男性思想"},{"pid":"31d1667a91da9269506f8d891b48c49c8e72b0c0","tid":355154,"uid":58161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T05:49:13.000Z","msg":"越爆越多 個校長一定係心理變態"},{"pid":"fe4b117687c9065adadf44872f423f0676a4ef01","tid":355154,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T05:50:26.000Z","msg":"大陸文化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n根本黃皮狗幾千年嘅劣根性一直都紮根係血入面，只係冇左西方文化思想拑制就會徹底爆發<br />\n哩廿年已經足夠證明華人黃皮狗基因本身就係卑賤無恥邪惡"},{"pid":"a16dc3a74e78334ebcf3612f7d4cbb30bedab157","tid":355154,"uid":83927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T05:53:14.000Z","msg":"唔比利是就冇運行"},{"pid":"f7f4794058c620c9221f584e01446f7333fc0b59","tid":355154,"uid":19267,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T05:54:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n[img]space[/img] </blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/cTmbnsX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FcTmbnsX.jpg&h=942dd680&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌你布歐咁可愛你攞個肥閪嚟比？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd788473534844d64403407c7619872506987e34","tid":355154,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T05:54:43.000Z","msg":"最恐怖全體老師配合<br />\n<br />\n教畜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbbbd5ff45781238cb723446fdc1a663048192dd","tid":355154,"uid":25125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T06:08:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05fd18340a14579d59640242fc15ab2d965382d9","tid":355154,"uid":25125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T06:47:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c0db92e93f6b23efaaa26fb25eb08b6ced1aaf4","tid":355154,"uid":2772,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T06:51:37.000Z","msg":"支那人就抵撚死既"}]}